]

# TaskDeletedText(IsDeleteAll, ListType, TaskContent)
- IF: ${IsDeleteAll != null}
  - ${AfterAllTasksDeletedText(ListType)}
- ELSE:
  - ${AfterTaskDeletedText(TaskContent, ListType)}

# AfterAllTasksDeletedText(ListType)
- I cleared your ${ListType} list.

# AfterTaskDeletedText(TaskContent, ListType)
- I deleted ${TaskContent} from your ${ListType} list. You don't have anything in your ${ListType} list now.

# DeletionAllConfirmationRefusedText(TaskCount, ListType)
- OK, I didn't delete anything. There are ${TaskCount} items on your ${ListType} list.

